## Retrieve a payment method

> Sample Request

```json
{
  "unbillKey": "<%= config.auth %>",
  "userId": "56e1ddbd1a05319bc198d36f"
}
```

> 200 Credit Card Response

```json
{
  "card": {
    "number": "XXXX0005",
    "brand": "american express",
    "type": "credit",
    "expDate": "2019-06-01T12:00:00.000Z"
  },
  "status": "verified"
}
```

> 200 Bank Account Response

```json
{
  "bank": {
    "routingNumber": "XXXX0002",
    "accountNumber": "XXXX0021s",
    "type": "checking"
  },
  "status": "verified"
}
```

> 400 Response

```json
{
  "message": "Oddly enough, we couldn't load your payment info."
}
```

Retrieve the payment method on file for a user.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/payment/get`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`userId` | Unbill user ID.

### Returns

Returns either a card object or bank object. If no payment method is on file, a `400` status code will be returned with an error.
